Code For Selected Patterns
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
{File:QQQ_IS.txt  Index:5  Index Date:20150227  PL:75.00%  PS:25%  Trades:4  CL:1}

IF CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 3 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 3 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 2 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 1.4313102 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 1.2374702 %
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
{File:QQQ_IS.txt  Index:42  Index Date:20150227  PL:75.00%  PS:25%  Trades:4  CL:1}

IF HIGH OF 0 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 2 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 2 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 3 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 3 BARS AGO > OPEN OF 1 BARS AGO
AND OPEN OF 1 BARS AGO > LOW OF 0 BARS AGO
AND LOW OF 0 BARS AGO > LOW OF 2 BARS AGO
AND LOW OF 2 BARS AGO > LOW OF 3 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 1.4313102 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 1.2374702 %
